My appeal got accepted on an account I bug abused in 2006, so I've decided I'm going to auto air runes flat out until I get banned. So far in about three days I've got 230k air runes, and I have 5k essence left with 3m cash and 58 RC.
I be needing to know the best way to earn money quick enough for essence (Regular is sitting at about 57gp currently), please note that I read maddies thread and decided those methods r too dix and too much effort.
thxbi.
